[[size 2.5em]]**CONTACT US**[[/size]]
[[/div]]
~~~~
Here at Taco Bell^^®^^, guest feedback is very important, and we are pleased that you want to contact us. If your concern is not addressed on our Frequently Asked Questions page, please fill out the form below and Taco Bell^^®^^ will address your concerns with care, courtesy, and discretion.

[[size 15px]]**Full Name ***[[/size]]
[[div style="background-color: white; border: 1px solid grey; margin-left 1%; margin-right: 40%; padding-left: 2%; padding-right: 2%; text-align: left; color:black;"]]
{{Vera K. Garcia}}
[[/div]]

@@@@

